1
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,440
Master Wang

2
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:06,760
This thing is a curse, yet also a blessing

3
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:09,520
As long as you make an offering every three years

4
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:12,520
the Wang Family will prosper for a hundred years

5
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:13,600
Good

6
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,920
There is one more poor soul in this world

7
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,560
Too many innocent people have already died

8
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:50,000
Stop now. Once Wang Shengchang arrives

9
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,480
I'll help you get rid of him

10
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:54,000
I said my affairs are none of your concern

11
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,040
Meigu

12
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,160
Meigu

13
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,360
Meigu

14
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,200
Where is your master?

15
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,200
My master has gone traveling

16
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,880
Before she left, she instructed me

17
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,880
I am to perform the Wang Family's Cursed Day ritual

18
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,680
Well...

19
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,720
I wonder if Master Ai is confident

20
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,200
Over this past year

21
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:21,840
Everyone has seen what I am capable of

22
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:24,200
Besides, the ritual comes once every three years

23
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,560
It must not be delayed

24
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,760
In that case

25
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,360
then you shall handle it

26
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:33,680
I have fed that thing by the old custom

27
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:37,280
and prepared the finest offering

28
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:46,560
From today on, give that thing this every day

29
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,120
to drive the evil from him

30
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,600
so the Cursed Day ritual can be completed

31
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,400
I understand

32
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,040
What happened?

33
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,160
What happened?

34
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,800
A bunch of idiots

35
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,080
A bunch of idiots

36
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,040
How many times have I told you?

37
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,760
I told you to keep a close eye on him

38
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,760
And yet you let him escape

39
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,280
Hurry up and chase him

40
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,640
Go after him now

41
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,440
Yes

42
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,640
Listen well

43
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,200
If you do not bring him back

44
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,760
watch your heads

45
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,600
What brings Master Ai here today?

46
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:35,240
I just picked a fine feng shui site for Zheng Yu

47
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,240
to bury Li Zhong and Xiao Shen and his father

48
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,520
I passed by and came for a cup of tea

49
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:43,920
You have been rather close to Zheng Yu lately

50
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:46,720
What, Fifth Concubine, are you jealous?

51
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:51,200
Master Ai, if that is all, please leave

52
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,200
I heard Zheng Yu mention

53
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,200
that you and your sister were very close

54
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,480
What is that to you?

55
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:05,640
I know the Wang Family has a very unusual plot

56
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:09,800
There may be something there that interests you

57
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:11,520
You mean...

58
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,720
Please tell me the location, Master Ai

59
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:23,160
On Fengli Mountain, southwest of Nanwan Town

60
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,000
Fifth Concubine, you might try your luck there

61
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,680
Excuse me

62
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,480
Once you have settled your sister's remains

63
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,600
you should die with no regrets, should you not?

64
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,360
Why did you follow me here?

65
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,360
Not bad

66
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:14,720
You are quite skilled with the dagger I gave you

67
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,520
How did you know I came here?

68
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,960
Your maid was worried about you

69
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,960
so she came to find me

70
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,520
She said you came here alone

71
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,880
Did I not tell you

72
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,360
not to act rashly on your own?

73
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,040
This is my sister's bracelet

74
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,520
Judging by the corrosion on this silver bracelet

75
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:56,520
it has likely been here for at least two or three years

76
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,800
This place is covered in corpse grass

77
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:04,960
Your sister's remains should be somewhere here

78
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,760
That is not right

79
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,040
The corpse grass is far too dense

80
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,560
There must be more than one skeleton here

81
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,720
For corpse grass to grow this thick

82
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,320
it would take at least over ten years

83
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:05,480
Twelve years ago, a plague broke out

84
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,160
young girls vanished mysteriously

85
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,760
Everyone said Li Zhong did it

86
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,840
They framed my father

87
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:10,960
to cover up the truth

88
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,600
and made my father the scapegoat

89
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:15,360
Could these be those girls who vanished without a trace?

90
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,760
Master Ai told me about this place

91
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,040
How did Master Ai know about this place?

92
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:28,120
What exactly is her relationship with the Wang Family?

93
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:32,320
Why did the Wang Family kill so many innocents?

94
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,400
Watch out

95
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,720
Zheng Yu

96
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,280
Run
